Openyard-www Directory
------------------------------------------
For the first time in coding history, Openyard is going to be programmed using a framework (Silex) along with many of it's more common extensions such as Doctrine for Database (Mysql). We'll also be using Git (Github.com) for version control. We're going to use a Silex Code base and all Openyard directories are going to pre-fixed with 'openyard-'....